em_assets/steam/apps/2758210/extras/905e5be9a0f298ece923f792f4c98ac8.poster.avif?t=1764563151\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758210/extras/905e5be9a0f298ece923f792f4c98ac8.webm?t=1764563151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2758210/extras/905e5be9a0f298ece923f792f4c98ac8.mp4?t=1764563151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Good luck, body challengers!",
